== Takaray a sowal ==
maramod(結婚)

Maramod han niyam o 'Amis ko nika lacacay no fafa'inai ato fafahi.

O tataakay a demak no lalafo no loma' ko nika raramod i niyaro'.

Patata ko fal'elohay a maramoday to titi no fafoy ato 'epah a pakaen to lalomaan i loma'.

Mapapatakid ato mapapa'icep ko fal'elohay a maramoday.

Mitolon ko faki to fal'elohay a maramoday, ato pakalemed i tohnian.


